  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Media Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Job Purpose:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in full video production process, mainly on storyboarding and filming</li>\n  <li>Administering of Sysmex Academy Online portal</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Highly versed in assembling, operating, and maintaining cameras, lights, microphones, relevant production grip equipment and cellular live streaming gear and other technologies (if required)</li>\n  <li>Manage video shootings / photography for all CAO online training</li>\n  <li>Assist trainers where required in the preparation of equipment and facilities for shooting</li>\n  <li>Design and develop instructional materials, including storyboards, e-learning modules, learner guides, and assessments</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with trainers and other stakeholders to gather content and ensure accuracy</li>\n  <li>Evaluate and revise content based on feedback and learning outcomes</li>\n  <li>Maintain and update the local domain of CAO (customer online learning portal)</li>\n  <li>Any other additional related responsibilities and project as required by Superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Film, Media or equivalent</li>\n  <li>2 – 3 years’ experience in video filming</li>\n  <li>Possess relevant technical skills especially in video production</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, responsible, work well independently and in multi-disciplinary teams</li>\n  <li>Experience in storyboarding techniques to map out content structure, interactions, and visuals before development</li>\n  <li>Experience in use of e-learning authoring tools (e.g., Articulate Storyline, Rise, Adobe Captivate)</li>\n  <li>Work location: 115 Eunos Ave 3, Zhaolim Building, #02-05,Singapore 409839 (Walking distance to Paya Lebar MRT)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
